# 🎨 PT Record System Styling Rules

## 🎯 Design System Overview

This project uses **TailwindCSS** with a custom design system featuring modern gradients, glassmorphism effects, and responsive design patterns.

## 🌈 Color Palette

### Primary Colors
```css
primary: {
  50: '#f0f9ff',   /* Very light blue */
  100: '#e0f2fe',  /* Light blue */
  200: '#bae6fd',  /* Lighter blue */
  300: '#7dd3fc',  /* Light blue */
  400: '#38bdf8',  /* Blue */
  500: '#0ea5e9',  /* Base blue */
  600: '#0284c7',  /* Dark blue */
  700: '#0369a1',  /* Darker blue */
  800: '#075985',  /* Very dark blue */
  900: '#0c4a6e',  /* Darkest blue */
}
```

### Role-Based Color Themes
- **Admin Dashboard**: Blue gradient (`from-slate-50 via-blue-50 to-indigo-100`)
- **Trainer Dashboard**: Green gradient (`from-slate-50 via-green-50 to-emerald-100`)
- **Member Dashboard**: Purple/Pink gradient (`from-slate-50 via-purple-50 to-pink-100`)

