## 🎨 Dark Mode Considerations

While not currently implemented, the design system is prepared for dark mode:

```tsx
// Use semantic color classes
className="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-white"

// Gradient adjustments for dark mode
className="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-100 dark:from-gray-900 dark:to-blue-900"
```

## 📱 Mobile-First Approach

Always design for mobile first, then enhance for larger screens:

```tsx
// Mobile: Stack vertically, Desktop: Side by side
<div className="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">

// Mobile: Single column, Desktop: Multiple columns
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">

// Mobile: Smaller text, Desktop: Larger text
<h1 className="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl">
```